1. Go to this page: https://reactnative.dev/docs/environment-setup

    Choose either yarn or npm and then. For this build we are using yarn. 
    In your terminal write:
    -->  yarn global add expo-cli 

2. Download the folder template (similar to create-react-app but for react native)

    ==> expo init signal-clone-yt

3. In the termianl you will be given a bunch of options. 

Press enter on --> blank a minimal app as clean as an empty canvas

4. Cd into the folder and in the vsc termianl write:

    --> yarn start

